{"tid":1616641,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人！反抗！","createTime":"2019-10-03T13:23:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-03T14:49:52.000Z","uid":93540,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b134f32026a192e91b5ee3aa9ad83ae6fd538ed3","tid":1616641,"uid":93540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T13:23:11.000Z","msg":"我真係好想之後聽到香港人既下一句<br />\n係反抗而唔係加油<br />\n每次聽到人嗌香港人 都唔想接<br />\n因為覺得好多人嗌完加油就算 冇其他行動去反抗極權<br />\n而加緊急法 蒙面法殺到埋身<br />\n仲有好多人覺得冇所謂 最多咪攬炒<br />\n但佢呢招擺到明係針對我地<br />\n反抗啊香港人！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dc9fe774659bb0172c1513e64a2ccbc3094f9f4","tid":1616641,"uid":145225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T13:24:52.000Z","msg":"同意 連口號都叫唔啱談何真係反抗<br />\n要由口號叫起！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">十月四前哨戰 全民口罩<br />\n十月五遊行 全民面具</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"0073439d12dc916ffce75ac23fbdae431f2201a1","tid":1616641,"uid":93540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1dc9fe774659bb0172c1513e64a2ccbc3094f9f4","tid":1616641,"uid":145225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T13:24:52.000Z","msg":"同意 連口號都叫唔啱談何真係反抗<br />\n要由口號叫起！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">十月四前哨戰 全民口罩<br />\n十月五遊行 全民面具</span></span></strong>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T13:27:37.000Z","msg":"聽到人嗌香港人果陣  一齊帶頭嗌反抗啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9311c58b85bf146f51789c65d2fd0dd7a3ab18b","tid":1616641,"uid":281180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-03T14:49:52.000Z","msg":"反抗！"}]}